            <div class="number">09</div>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
            <h3>Medical Support</h3>
            <p>Assists hospitals and clinics in managing blood reserves effectively.</p>
            <div class="number">10</div>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
            <h3>Rare Blood Type Network</h3>
            <p>Builds a network of rare blood type donors for critical situations.</p>
            <div class="number">11</div>
